node.text: it is much more than just a timepiece. it’s got it all. ⌚ our Link Bracelet is water and sweat resistance. our Genuine Leather Watchband can be customized and is made out of biodegradable leather. they are all created for durability and all-day comfort, so you can go about your day, wherever it may lead. get yours only at #CASETiFY.

node.text:
did you know: it takes 𝙖𝙩 𝙡𝙚𝙖𝙨𝙩 450 years for a plastic bottle to completely degrade & over 80% of plastic bottles 𝙙𝙤 𝙣𝙤𝙩 get recycled. 😲⁠
that's a NO from us!🙅‍♀️🙅 keep single-use plastic bottles out of the waste system with our customizable Stainless Steel Water Bottle. with two sizes to choose from, find a print that speaks to you or make it your own with just a few taps!

node.text:
#SORAYAMAxCASETiFY collection focuses on hyperrealism as inspiration. capturing futuristic figures printed on mirror cases to emphasize the metallic accent @hajimesorayamaofficial uses in his artwork. did we mention, we have a limited edition stainless steel case inspired by his artwork - engraved with a collection number (only 250 created) and an 18-karat gold plate CASETiFY logo! 🔥 get on the list to find out more!⁠⁠⁠
⁠⁠⁠
#SORAYAMAxCASETiFY is launching on July 27th 4pm HKT, 1am PST.⁠⁠⁠
